.TH PRODBOX_pulumi 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-pulumi \- AWS validation stack lifecycle
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox pulumi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Pulumi-backed AWS validation stack commands.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBeks-resources\fR
Provision or inspect EKS test stack
.TP
\fBeks-destroy\fR
Destroy EKS test stack
.TP
\fBtest-resources\fR
Provision or inspect HA RKE2 test stack
.TP
\fBtest-destroy\fR
Destroy HA RKE2 test stack
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox pulumi eks-resources\fR
Reconcile the EKS validation stack.
